description: The Boba Truck! is a state of the art mobile tea and coffee brewery that will be serving Southern California.  Our exclusive process allows us to brew each drink to order one at a time. This ensures that you are drinking the freshest possible tea with all the flavors and anti-oxidants intact. Because your drink is brewed and made to order, the tea strength and sweetness is also fully adjustable. Every drink can be enjoyed hot or iced.
name: The Boba Truck!
